reviewText: Two funny movies for a great price.
Bonus to get two movies for the price of one. Came on time and package wasn't damaged. Thank you.
My sister and I love these movies and quote them all the time. They are not your average comedy but they are comedy classics.
The movie didn't play the ending, and I never got to finish it. The other movie was good over all.

They thought it through right to put these two together. They're both must haves in any collection. Note: One is rated R and one is PG-13, they aren't the same rating just because they're packaged together.
